  * MQTT IoT/Smart Home Plugin: Full implementation with libmosquitto
    (Phase 1-4: connect/subscribe/publish, bot conversation, alerts,
    bridge, sparklines, QoS, MQTT 5.0). 52 unit tests.
  * MUC Close Fix: Titlebar menu and Ctrl+W now properly leave MUC rooms.
  * MUC Race Condition Fix: Removed Idle.add() wrapper for part().
  * BotManager: No more warnings when Botmother API not running.
  * OMEMO: Preserve device trust on chat-clear.
  * CI: MQTT plugin now built in all CI workflows (AppImage, Flatpak, Windows).

